2️⃣ Fix Users Table (Important)

Replace your users migration with this:

Schema::create('users', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();

    $table->string('name');
    $table->string('email')->unique();
    $table->string('password');

    $table->foreignId('role_id')->constrained('roles')->cascadeOnDelete();

    $table->timestamps();
});

Problem you had:

role_name ❌

Correct:

role_id ✅
3️⃣ Create Menus Table

Run command:

php artisan make:migration create_menus_table

Paste this:

Schema::create('menus', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();
    $table->string('name');
    $table->string('slug');
    $table->timestamps();
});

Example menus:

id	name	slug
