4️⃣ Create Role Menu Access Table

This table will control which role can access which menu.

Run:

php artisan make:migration create_role_menu_access_table

Migration:

Schema::create('role_menu_access', function (Blueprint $table) {
    $table->id();

    $table->foreignId('role_id')->constrained('roles')->cascadeOnDelete();
    $table->foreignId('menu_id')->constrained('menus')->cascadeOnDelete();

    $table->timestamps();
});
5️⃣ Sellers Table

Run:

php artisan make:migration create_sellers_table

Code:

Schema::create('sellers', function (Blueprint $table) {
